Package: thirtDIF
Title: DIF Testing Implementation for thirt
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Maxwell", "Box", , "boxm.psy@outlook.com", role = c("cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: thirtDIF is an extension of thirt (Nguyen & Nydick, 2024), 
expanding functionality for differential item functioning (DIF) in Thurstonian 
Forced-Choice Item Response Theory (T-FCIRT) models. thirtDIF adapts Lee et al., 
(2024)'s methodology for conducting DIF testing in T-IRT models. Functionality for 
both statistical significance and practical effect testing of DIF is included. 
